<!-- qx-element-text --><div id="qx-text-855" class="qx-element qx-element-text  qx-text-left" >
  <p><span style="font-size: 12pt;">Q: What is required to host a masternode?</span><br /><span style="font-size: 12pt;"> A: About 200'000 XSH(estimate) and a server with a dedicated IP and ~100% uptime.</span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 12pt;">Q: When do we get new exchanges?</span><br /><span style="font-size: 12pt;"> A: As soon as CE or kucoin responds we will join them, we are also still contacting other exchanges</span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 12pt;">Q: When will (a certain feature) be released?</span><br /><span style="font-size: 12pt;"> A: Check the roadmap at <span style="color: #ffcc00;"><a style="color: #ffcc00;" href="../index.php/roadmap">https://www.shieldcurrency.com/Roadmap/</a></span> and <span style="color: #ffcc00;"><a style="color: #ffcc00;" href="../index.php/roadmap">https://www.shieldcurrency.com/Projects/</a></span></span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 12pt;">Q: How many members does the team have?</span><br /><span style="font-size: 12pt;"> A: 5</span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 12pt;">Q: When will the whitepaper be out?</span><br /><span style="font-size: 12pt;"> A: It's already released: <span style="color: #ffcc00;"><a style="color: #ffcc00;" href="../index.php/whitepaper">https://shieldcurrency.com/Whitepaper/</a></span></span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 12pt;">Q: How do I mine SHIELD?</span><br /><span style="font-size: 12pt;"> A: You can get started with the following wiki page, and clarify any further questions you may have in #mining: <span style="color: #ffcc00;"><a style="color: #ffcc00;" href="https://git.io/SHIELDwiki-mining">https://git.io/SHIELDwiki-mining</a></span></span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 12pt;">Q: My QT/CMD wallet is taking hours to sync, help!</span><br /><span style="font-size: 12pt;"> A: You can use the downloadable blockchain from <span style="color: #ffcc00;"><a style="color: #ffcc00;" href="https://git.io/SHIELDblockchain">https://git.io/SHIELDblockchain</a></span> to speed up the process. Adding nodes from <span style="color: #ffcc00;"><a style="color: #ffcc00;" href="https://blockstats.pw/shield/addnode/">https://blockstats.pw/shield/addnode/</a></span> also helps</span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 12pt;">Q: Which quantum proof algo will be used?</span><br /><span style="font-size: 12pt;"> A: We are still choosing between Winternitz and BLISS signatures</span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 12pt;"> Q: When will p2p tipping be made</span><br /><span style="font-size: 12pt;"> A: It's part of the integrate so that will be begin Q2 2018</span></p>
